    <h3>Key Features to Consider</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Video Quality:</strong> 1080p minimum, 4K for best detail</li>
        <li><strong>Night Vision:</strong> Color night vision provides better identification</li>
        <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Local storage vs cloud subscriptions</li>
        <li><strong>Power Source:</strong> Battery, solar, or wired options</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Features:</strong> Person/vehicle detection, package alerts</li>
        <li><strong>Integration:</strong> Works with Alexa, Google Assistant, Apple HomeKit</li>
    </ul>
